00:31:52,680 --> 00:31:53,1000
aggressive empire.

848
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:55,770
So in the Western Empire at this time,

849
00:31:55,769 --> 00:31:59,099
you have two sort of rival groups.

850
00:31:59,099 --> 00:31:59,969
And they're very different

