00:32:25,349 --> 00:32:27,869
They make their money through maritime trade.

861
00:32:27,869 --> 00:32:30,779
So they have ships that go all over the Mediterranean.

862
00:32:30,779 --> 00:32:33,928
They don't have a large army of Carthaginians;

