00:32:40,920 --> 00:32:42,630
You know, it's different philosophies,

866
00:32:42,630 --> 00:32:45,060
different economies, everything.

867
00:32:45,059 --> 00:32:47,728
Rome is strong on land, Carthage is strong at sea,

868
00:32:47,730 --> 00:32:49,619
so there's this dichotomy.

