00:33:40,289 --> 00:33:42,329
And I think, in the course of the wars

894
00:33:42,329 --> 00:33:45,239
between Rome and Carthage called the Punic Wars,

895
00:33:45,240 --> 00:33:47,940
there's this geographic inevitability to them.

