00:37:34,079 --> 00:37:36,779
This is the furnace that Rome passes through

999
00:37:36,780 --> 00:37:38,159
that is the dividing point

1000
00:37:38,159 --> 00:37:40,889
between when they're one more up and coming empire

1001
00:37:40,889 --> 00:37:43,199
and when they're clearly the dominant power

1002
00:37:43,199 --> 00:37:44,848
in the Mediterranean.

