00:38:45,510 --> 00:38:47,789
And the Romans won't give it to 'em.

1032
00:38:47,789 --> 00:38:49,769
They've been attacking all these other areas

1033
00:38:49,769 --> 00:38:52,048
and chipping away at Carthaginian power.

1034
00:38:52,050 --> 00:38:55,050
So finally, after more than a decade in Italy,

1035
00:38:55,050 --> 00:38:57,869
Hannibal is called back to defend the homeland,

1036
00:38:57,869 --> 00:38:59,819
defend Carthage from Scipio.

1037
00:38:59,820 --> 00:39:01,590
The two meet in a big battle.

1038
00:39:01,590 --> 00:39:03,599
This should be one of the great battles of all times,

1039
00:39:03,599 --> 00:39:04,469
the Battle of Zama,

1040
00:39:04,469 --> 00:39:06,629
but, you know, Hannibal's guys

