00:41:43,230 --> 00:41:45,149
And it's just using the terrain,

1113
00:41:45,150 --> 00:41:45,983
understanding this,

1114
00:41:45,983 --> 00:41:48,149
again, Hannibal's very much outnumbered,

1115
00:41:48,150 --> 00:41:50,130
but he's able to use the terrain

