00:41:58,469 --> 00:42:00,658
So the traditional thing you do in the ancient world

1119
00:42:00,659 --> 00:42:02,369
is the two armies would line up

1120
00:42:02,369 --> 00:42:04,079
on opposite sides of a field,

1121
00:42:04,079 --> 00:42:05,849
