00:44:12,300 --> 00:44:13,709
- The ancient world,

1183
00:44:13,710 --> 00:44:16,290
sort of from the Greeks through the Romans,

1184
00:44:16,289 --> 00:44:21,289
there's this consistent line of focusing on heavy infantry.

1185
00:44:21,539 --> 00:44:23,218
So going back to Greece

1186
00:44:23,219 --> 00:44:25,138
when they're fighting, let's say, Persia,

