1711
01:03:16,409 --> 01:03:18,179
he marries a Persian woman,

1712
01:03:18,179 --> 01:03:20,909
he sort of forces thousands of his troops

1713
01:03:20,909 --> 01:03:22,439
to marry local women,

1714
01:03:22,440 --> 01:03:24,899
he appoints Persians to positions of power,

1715
01:03:24,900 --> 01:03:27,840
he integrates Persian units into his military.

1716
01:03:27,840 --> 01:03:30,960
He really wanted to fuse all these things together.

1717
01:03:30,960 --> 01:03:35,160
