02:56:18,780 --> 02:56:19,620
they had to decide, well,

4754
02:56:19,620 --> 02:56:21,689
what are we gonna do with these provinces?

4755
02:56:21,690 --> 02:56:23,1000
And they, in the end, settled on this notion of

4756
02:56:24,000 --> 02:56:25,830
we'll put a Roman governor in charge,

4757
02:56:25,829 --> 02:56:27,958
we'll collect some sort of taxes.

4758
02:56:27,959 --> 02:56:31,168
But they often didn't collect the taxes directly.

4759
02:56:31,170 --> 02:56:33,509
Instead, they would sell contracts

4760
02:56:33,510 --> 02:56:36,750
to private businesses to collect taxes.

4761
02:56:36,750 --> 02:56:38,707
So the private businesses would bid and say,

4762
02:56:38,707 --> 02:56:40,469
"All right, if you give us the contract

4763
02:56:40,469 --> 02:56:42,329
to collect taxes in Sicily,

4764
02:56:42,329 --> 02:56:44,518
we'll give you X number of money up front,

4765
02:56:44,520 --> 02:56:45,570
and then we go out

4766
02:56:45,569 --> 02:56:49,198
and try to collect enough to make back that money

4767
02:56:49,200 --> 02:56:50,940
and make ourselves a profit."

4768
02:56:50,940 --> 02:56:52,770
And this is a terrible system

4769
02:56:52,770 --> 02:56:54,240
because, obviously, they're gonna go and try

4770
02:56:54,239 --> 02:56:57,538
and squeeze as much as they can out of Sicily.

4771
02:56:57,540 --> 02:57:01,189
And these companies were called publicans, publicani.

4772
02:57:02,077 --> 02:57:03,478
And in the Bible, there's a phrase,

4773
02:57:03,479 --> 02:57:05,158
publicans and sinners,

4774
02:57:05,159 --> 02:57:08,399
and that should give you an idea how they're viewed.

4775
02:57:08,399 --> 02:57:10,649
So everybody hated these tax collectors,

4776
02:57:10,649 --> 02:57:13,079
and it was a really kind of dumb system

4777
02:57:13,079 --> 02:57:16,288
because, you know, the publicans are going out

4778
02:57:16,290 --> 02:57:18,330
and squeezing way more than they should

4779
02:57:18,329 --> 02:57:20,998
in an unhealthy way from the provinces.

4780
02:57:21,000 --> 02:57:23,702
And the Roman state was doing this kind of weird thing

4781
02:57:23,702 --> 02:57:25,738
that they should have been doing themselves.

4782
02:57:25,739 --> 02:57:27,299
And over time, that shifts a bit

4783
