02:57:32,819 --> 02:57:34,468
So it's like, okay, we're taxing you.

4786
02:57:34,469 --> 02:57:36,808
You pay it in wheat if you're a farmer or something.

4787
02:57:36,809 --> 02:57:38,759
Not necessarily in cash.

4788
02:57:38,760 --> 02:57:40,679
So it was in, in many ways,

4789
02:57:40,680 --> 02:57:44,970
the Roman economy is under underdeveloped.

4790
02:57:44,969 --> 02:57:47,578
They didn't have a lot of the sophisticated systems

4791
