that we have today,

4792
02:57:48,540 --> 02:57:51,780
and it probably held them back in some ways.

4793
02:57:51,780 --> 02:57:54,960
And, again, they have that resistance to change.

4794
02:57:54,959 --> 02:57:57,249
The Romans also had weird notions about

4795
02:57:58,620 --> 02:58:00,930
