is farming.

4799
02:58:07,920 --> 02:58:11,370
So, you know, rich Romans would get involved

4800
02:58:11,370 --> 02:58:12,930
in what we would call business.

4801
02:58:12,930 --> 02:58:14,069
You know, manufacturing,

4802
02:58:14,069 --> 02:58:16,499
