4803
02:58:16,500 --> 02:58:17,430
But they would often do it

4804
02:58:17,430 --> 02:58:19,979
through sort of front companies or employees

4805
02:58:19,979 --> 02:58:22,168
who did it on their behalf, officially,

4806
02:58:22,170 --> 02:58:23,730
and then they sort of funnel the profits

4807
02:58:23,729 --> 02:58:24,749
