So you have a series of these kind of army emperors,

4906
03:01:54,059 --> 03:01:55,409
who are just good generals,

4907
03:01:55,409 --> 03:01:58,679
who managed to push the barbarians out,

4908
03:01:58,680 --> 03:02:00,573
reestablish the borders.

