5483
03:23:20,819 --> 03:23:21,988
- Being posted to an area

5484
03:23:21,989 --> 03:23:24,868
where they eat these terrible foreign foods.

5485
03:23:24,870 --> 03:23:27,050
And of course the cliche for the Romans

5486
03:23:27,049 --> 03:23:30,328
