5510
03:24:10,530 --> 03:24:11,820
you tend to stay in one place,

5511
03:24:11,819 --> 03:24:13,198
you tend to build cities.

5512
03:24:13,200 --> 03:24:15,749
If you're following herds of cows around,

5513
03:24:15,750 --> 03:24:17,580
you don't build cities.

5514
03:24:17,579 --> 03:24:19,498
You have a totally different lifestyle.

5515
03:24:19,500 --> 03:24:20,970
So it's diet,

5516
03:24:20,969 --> 03:24:23,759
but it's more fundamental underlying things

5517
03:24:23,760 --> 03:24:25,380
about your entire culture.

