nuclear weapons change war?

5572
03:26:23,370 --> 03:26:24,900
- Yeah, I mean, that's the,

5573
03:26:24,899 --> 03:26:28,198
now we can destroy the world

5574
03:26:28,200 --> 03:26:31,709
and truly kind of destroy civilizations wholesale,

5575
03:26:31,709 --> 03:26:34,378
and that does seem to be a new thing.

5576
03:26:34,379 --> 03:26:37,408
I mean, no matter what the Romans do, did,

5577
03:26:37,409 --> 03:26:39,058
they didn't have that choice,

5578
03:26:39,059 --> 03:26:39,906
that ability to think,

5579
03:26:39,906 --> 03:26:42,752
"I can do something that will end,

5580
03:26:43,860 --> 03:26:45,330
you know, life as we know it,

5581
03:26:45,329 --> 03:26:47,125
at least, on the planet."

5582
03:26:48,360 --> 03:26:50,582
And that's a very different perspective.

5583
03:26:51,959 --> 03:26:54,051
And it's, I think, weird and interesting moment right now.

5584
03:26:54,052 --> 03:26:56,669
I mean, I'm getting way beyond ancient history here,

