03:26:56,670 --> 03:26:57,839
but, you know, for a long time,

5586
03:26:57,840 --> 03:27:00,869
we had this sort of stasis with the nuclear standoff,

5587
03:27:00,870 --> 03:27:03,390
with mutually assured destruction

5588
03:27:03,389 --> 03:27:06,839
between this US sort of block of nations

5589
03:27:06,840 --> 03:27:08,729
and the Soviet ones.

