03:27:13,950 --> 03:27:16,530
are gonna start becoming nuclear capable.

5594
03:27:16,530 --> 03:27:17,939
We might have a resurgence

5595
03:27:17,940 --> 03:27:20,399
of just building new weapons platforms,

5596
03:27:20,399 --> 03:27:22,288
with China seems very eager

5597
03:27:22,290 --> 03:27:24,060
to expand their nuclear arsenal

5598
03:27:24,059 --> 03:27:25,438
in all sorts of ways.

5599
03:27:25,440 --> 03:27:29,279
So it's a unnerving time, let's say, right now.

5600
03:27:29,280 --> 03:27:31,530
- And it's a terrifying experiment

5601
03:27:31,530 --> 03:27:34,679
to find out if nuclear weapons,

5602
03:27:34,680 --> 03:27:36,510
when a lot of nations have nuclear weapons,

5603
03:27:36,510 --> 03:27:40,627
is that going to enforce civility and peace

5604
03:27:40,627 --> 03:27:42,719
or is it going to be a destabilizing

5605
03:27:42,719 --> 03:27:44,579
and, ultimately, civilization destroying?

5606
03:27:44,579 --> 03:27:46,889
- Right. I mean, it was weirdly stable

5607
03:27:46,889 --> 03:27:48,479
when it was a bipolar world,

5608
03:27:48,479 --> 03:27:50,339
where you had just sort of those two blocks.

5609
03:27:50,340 --> 03:27:52,710
Now, with a multipolar world

5610
03:27:52,709 --> 03:27:54,778
with access to these weapons, I don't know.

5611
03:27:54,780 --> 03:27:56,760
I mean, we're kind of jumping out the ancient world,

5612
03:27:56,760 --> 03:27:58,649
but I'll tell you one thing that's always fascinated me

5613
03:27:58,649 --> 03:28:01,198
in this sort of comparison, ancient-modern,

5614
03:28:01,200 --> 03:28:05,099
is how people don't learn the lessons of the past

5615
03:28:05,100 --> 03:28:06,539
in military history.

5616
03:28:06,540 --> 03:28:08,189
And the very specific example

5617
03:28:08,190 --> 03:28:11,160
that in my lifetime I've seen play out twice

5618
03:28:11,159 --> 03:28:13,589
is, just certain places,

5619
03:28:13,590 --> 03:28:15,750
people make the same mistakes over and over again.

5620
03:28:15,750 --> 03:28:19,319
So a nice example is Afghanistan.

5621
03:28:19,319 --> 03:28:21,988
Or roughly, that sort of Northern Pakistan

5622
03:28:21,989 --> 03:28:24,448
slash into what is Afghanistan.

5623
03:28:24,450 --> 03:28:27,390
I mean, that is a geographic region

5624
03:28:27,389 --> 03:28:29,609
that over and over again,

5625
03:28:29,610 --> 03:28:32,969
the best, most sophisticated armies in the world

5626
03:28:32,969 --> 03:28:36,689
have invaded and have met horrible failure.

5627
03:28:36,690 --> 03:28:38,400
And that goes all the way back to, you know,

5628
03:28:38,399 --> 03:28:41,698
Alexander the Great tried to conquer that area,

5629
03:28:41,700 --> 03:28:43,650
the Mongols tried to do it,

5630
03:28:43,649 --> 03:28:45,209
the Huns tried to do it,

5631
03:28:45,209 --> 03:28:47,699
the Moguls tried to do it,

5632
03:28:47,700 --> 03:28:50,459
you know, Victorian Britain tried to do it,

5633
03:28:50,459 --> 03:28:52,439
the Russians tried to do it,

5634
03:28:52,440 --> 03:28:54,089
the Americans tried to do it,

5635
03:28:54,090 --> 03:28:56,909
and they made the very same mistakes

5636
03:28:56,909 --> 03:28:59,069
over and over and over again.

5637
03:28:59,069 --> 03:29:02,009
And the two mistakes are not understanding the terrain,

5638
03:29:02,010 --> 03:29:04,740
that it's a rocky mountainous area,

5639
03:29:04,739 --> 03:29:07,529
that people can always hide in caves;

5640
03:29:07,530 --> 03:29:08,640
and it's not understanding

5641
03:29:08,639 --> 03:29:11,609
the fundamentally tribal nature of that area,

5642
03:29:11,610 --> 03:29:13,739
that that's where the real allegiance is,

5643
03:29:13,739 --> 03:29:14,878
is in these tribes,

5644
03:29:14,879 --> 03:29:17,099
it's not an a centralized government.

5645
03:29:17,100 --> 03:29:19,350
And that's the same error Alexander made

5646
03:29:19,350 --> 03:29:21,600
as, you know, the British made

5647
03:29:21,600 --> 03:29:23,249
in the 19th century,

5648
03:29:23,250 --> 03:29:25,649
as the Russians, as the Americans.

5649
03:29:25,649 --> 03:29:27,568
And it's just, it's so depressing

5650
03:29:27,569 --> 03:29:30,509
as a historian who studies history

5651
03:29:30,510 --> 03:29:33,510
to see these things being repeated over and over again

5652
03:29:33,510 --> 03:29:36,269
and you know exactly what's gonna happen.

