03:30:46,020 --> 03:30:48,450
- The calendar. - The calendar.

5680
03:30:48,450 --> 03:30:49,283
The words.

5681
03:30:49,282 --> 03:30:50,729
We're using Julius Caesar's calendar.

5682
03:30:50,729 --> 03:30:52,889
I mean, Pope Gregory did one tiny little twist,

5683
03:30:52,889 --> 03:30:54,419
but Caesar's the one who basically came up

5684
03:30:54,420 --> 03:30:55,320
with our current calendar,

5685
03:30:55,319 --> 03:30:58,019
with 365 days, 12 months,

5686
03:30:58,020 --> 03:30:59,433
leap years, all that.

5687
03:31:00,299 --> 03:31:02,939
You know, so we're living in law.

5688
03:31:02,940 --> 03:31:05,790
There's just no way to escape the power of the past.

5689
03:31:05,790 --> 03:31:08,879
And what I believe very ardently

5690
03:31:08,879 --> 03:31:13,199
is that you can't make good decisions in the present

5691
03:31:13,200 --> 03:31:15,869
and you can't make good decisions about the future

5692
03:31:15,870 --> 03:31:17,820
without understanding the past.

5693
03:31:17,819 --> 03:31:19,738
And that's not just true with your own life,

5694
03:31:19,739 --> 03:31:21,299
but it's in understanding others.

5695
03:31:21,299 --> 03:31:23,443
So it's not only your own past you have to understand,

5696
03:31:23,443 --> 03:31:24,779
but you have to understand other people,

5697
03:31:24,780 --> 03:31:26,280
what's influencing them.

