03:31:30,270 --> 03:31:31,649
And the answer to where they're coming from

5701
03:31:31,649 --> 03:31:33,658
is where they came from,

5702
03:31:33,659 --> 03:31:34,949
and what shaped them,

5703
03:31:34,950 --> 03:31:36,900
and what forces affect them.

5704
03:31:36,899 --> 03:31:38,818
So I think it's absolutely vital

5705
03:31:38,819 --> 03:31:41,339
to have some understanding of the past

5706
03:31:41,340 --> 03:31:45,780
in order to make competent decisions in the present.

